reviewText:
"HOW WILL MOTHER GOOSE EVER TEACH HER SON,
Simon Goose,
the art of rhyming?
Who will carry on the great Goose tradition of rhyming rhymes?
You'll have great fun,
seeing just how it's done,
with some surprising advice from Grandmother Goose!

Everyone's favorite childhood rhymes are here,
infused with Wegman's wry sense of humor and charm and played by his famous canine companions:
Betty, Crooky, Chundo and Chip!"
[from the back cover of VHS case]
